-- page: Introduction to doc-site

‚ö°Ô∏è `doc-site` will help you create a beautiful documentation site in no time.

üßê It helps you to build a static documentation with fast client-side
navigation, leveraging the full power of fastn to make your documentation site
interactive.

It provides out-of-the-box documentation features that can be used to create any
kind of site(personal website, blog, etc).

-- h2: Fast Track üöÄ

Create your first `doc-site` project in just 5 minutes!

 [Click here](https://github.com/fastn-stack/fastn-template/) to use `doc-site`
for your fastn project.

-- h2: üëÄ Want to learn more?

Feel free to check [our expander course](https://fastn.com/expander/) or jump
into our [FifthTry Discord server](https://discord.gg/bucrdvptYd).

